    "## Feature 9: Digital Footprint Scanner â€” Pre-Deployment\n",
    "\n",
    "The `DigitalFootprintScanner` collects multi-dimensional digital evidence of attacks across the full ML lifecycle.\n",
    "\n",
    "**Pre-deployment signals (training stage):**\n",
    "- Model weight integrity â€” SHA-256 hash verification (MITRE AML.T0018)\n",
    "- Supply chain attacks â€” typosquatting and known malicious packages (MITRE AML.T0010)\n",
    "- Process injection â€” unexpected child processes (MITRE AML.T0011)\n",
    "- Network exfiltration â€” unexpected outbound connections (MITRE AML.T0024)\n",
    "\n",
    "All events are tagged with MITRE ATLAS technique IDs for compliance reporting.\n"
   ],
   "execution_count": null,
   "outputs": []
